---
// Features section with SVG illustrations
---

<section id="features" class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-zinc-900 border-b dark:border-zinc-800 py-8">
  <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto m-8">
    <h2
      class="w-full my-2 text-5xl font-black leading-tight text-center text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100"
    >
      Features
    </h2>
    <div class="w-full mb-4">
      <div
        class="h-1 mx-auto gradient w-64 opacity-25 my-0 py-0 rounded-t"
      ></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-5/6 sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
          Read Anywhere
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Boris works on any device. Whether you prefer to read on desktop, mobile, or tablet, Boris is there for you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          If you install boris as a PWA, you can read and highlight on your phone or tablet as if it was a native app.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <img src="/read-anywhere.svg" alt="Read Anywhere" class="w-full sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <img src="/distraction-free.svg" alt="Distraction-Free" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <div class="align-middle">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
            Distraction-Free
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Boris aims to be a calm reader app with clean typography, beautiful design, and a focus on readability.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Boris does not and will never have ads, trackers, paywalls, subscriptions, or any other distractions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-5/6 sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
          Airplane Mode
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Boris is offline‑first by design. With a local relay you can read,
          create highlights, and browse your library without a network. Flight
          Mode stores changes locally and syncs later.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Run <a href="https://github.com/greenart7c3/Citrine" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Citrine</a> on your phone or <a href="https://github.com/CodyTseng/nostr-relay-tray" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">nostr-relay-tray</a> on your desktop to use Boris offline.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <img src="/airplane-mode.svg" alt="Airplane Mode" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <img src="/swarm-highlights.svg" alt="Social Highlights" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <div class="align-middle">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
            Social Highlights
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            See highlights from you, your friends, and the wider nostrverse —
            all in one place. Toggle levels, jump to passages, and discover
            great reads. Powered by <a href="https://nostrbook.dev/kinds/9802" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">NIP‑84 (kind 9802)</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <img src="/zap-splits.svg" alt="Zap Splits" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <div class="align-middle">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
            Zap Splits
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            When creating highlights, Boris automatically sets up zap splits so that value flows to authors and curators alike.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            You have full control over all zap splits. You can change the splits as you wish or use one of the predefined presets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-5/6 sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
          Comforting Colors
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Read during the day or late at night. 
          Boris has multiple light and dark themes tuned for long reads.
          Choose fonts and sizes, highlight styles, and pick colors that fit your personal choice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <img src="/comforting-colors.svg" alt="Comforting Colors" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <img src="/peace-of-mind.svg" alt="Peace of Mind" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
        <div class="align-middle">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
            Peace of Mind
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            No signups, no accounts, no lock-ins. Your data lives on Nostr, and
            Boris renders it locally through an opinionated lens.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
            You will never be locked out, no matter what. Boris will never
            rugpull you, because it can't rugpull you. You are in full control
            of your data. All the highlights, bookmarks, and reading metadata
            you create will forever be your own.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="w-5/6 sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
          Free as in Freedom
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Boris is free and open‑source and always will be.
          You can do with it what you want.
          Fork it, modify it, contribute to it, or just use it as is.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Boris is free as in beer too, but you can send me sats if you appreciate my work.
          <a href="https://dergigi.com/support/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">#v4v</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6">
        <img src="/free-forever.svg" alt="Free Forever" class="w-5/6 sm:h-64 mx-auto" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

